title: "I Don't Think So, Honey! 2" LIVE (Part One)
itunes:title: "I Don't Think So, Honey! 2" LIVE (Part One)
description:
Las Culturistas "I Don't Think So, Honey" returns for its SECOND LIVE SHOW! 50 of New York's best comedians take one minute each to go off on culture. Part One featuring: Nicole Silverberg, Nicole Spiezio, Keisha Zollar, Michael Kayne, Lauren Adams, Peter Smith, Molly Austin, Jaboukie Young-White, Max Wittert, Lorelei Ramirez, Hallie Haas, Jason Gore, Moujan Zolfaghari, Douglas Widick, Kristen Bartlett, Tallie Medel, Jasmine Pierce, Eleanore Pienta, Beth Newell, Sunita Mani, Greta Titelman, Drew Anderson, Amanda Duarte, and Michelle Buteau. Hosted by Matt Rogers & Bowen Yang!

Recorded 8/11/17 at Littlefield in Brooklyn, NY.
